            "content": "1988年数学（一）真题解析"
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "bbox": [
                0.06,
                0.138,
                0.092,
                0.15
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "一、"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.06,
                0.156,
                0.717,
                0.19
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(1)【解】 由 \\(\\lim_{n\\to \\infty}\\left|\\frac{a_{n + 1}}{a_n}\\right| = \\lim_{n\\to \\infty}\\frac{1}{(n + 1)\\cdot 3^{n + 1}}\\Bigg{/}\\frac{1}{n\\cdot 3^n} = \\frac{1}{3}\\) ，得收敛半径 \\(R = 3\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.092,
                0.197,
                0.48,
                0.228
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "当 \\(x - 3 = -3\\) ，即 \\(x = 0\\) 时， \\(\\sum_{n = 1}^{\\infty}\\frac{(-1)^n}{n}\\) 收敛；"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.092,
                0.237,
                0.425,
                0.267
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "当 \\(x - 3 = 3\\) ，即 \\(x = 6\\) 时， \\(\\sum_{n = 1}^{\\infty}\\frac{1}{n}\\) 发散，"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.091,
                0.276,
                0.411,
                0.306
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "故级数 \\(\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty} \\frac{(x-3)^n}{n \\cdot 3^n}\\) 的收敛域为 \\([0,6)\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.06,
                0.317,
                0.514,
                0.334
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(2)【解】 由 \\(\\mathrm{e}^{\\varphi^2 (x)} = 1 - x\\) ，得 \\(\\varphi (x) = \\sqrt{\\ln(1 - x)}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.091,
                0.341,
                0.455,
                0.354
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "由 \\(1 - x \\geqslant 1\\) 得 \\(\\varphi(x)\\) 的定义域为 \\((- \\infty, 0]\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.06,
                0.362,
                0.27,
                0.377
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（3）【解】 由高斯公式得"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.208,
                0.384,
                0.703,
                0.447
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\begin{array}{l} I = \\oiint_ {S} x ^ {3} d y d z + y ^ {3} d z d x + z ^ {3} d x d y = 3 \\iiint_ {a} (x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} + z ^ {2}) d v \\\\ = 3 \\int_ {0} ^ {2 \\pi} d \\theta \\int_ {0} ^ {\\pi} d \\varphi \\int_ {0} ^ {1} r ^ {4} \\sin \\varphi d r = \\frac {6 \\pi}{5} \\int_ {0} ^ {\\pi} \\sin \\varphi d \\varphi = \\frac {1 2 \\pi}{5}. \\\\ \\end{array}\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "bbox": [
                0.06,
                0.456,
                0.149,
                0.471
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "二、填空题"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.06,
                0.477,
                0.265,
                0.493
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(1)【答案】 \\((1 + 2t)\\mathrm{e}^{2t}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.09,
                0.499,
                0.611,
                0.528
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(f(t) = \\lim_{x\\to \\infty}t\\left(1 + \\frac{1}{x}\\right)^{2tx} = t\\lim_{x\\to \\infty}\\left[\\left(1 + \\frac{1}{x}\\right)^x\\right]^{2t} = te^{2t},\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.091,
                0.535,
                0.395,
                0.55
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "则 \\(f^{\\prime}(t) = \\mathrm{e}^{2t} + 2t\\mathrm{e}^{2t} = (1 + 2t)\\mathrm{e}^{2t}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.06,
                0.559,
                0.203,
                0.586
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(2)【答案】 \\(\\frac{3}{2}\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.09,
                0.595,
                0.469,
                0.609
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(f(x)\\) 的傅里叶级数在 \\(x = 1\\) 处收敛于"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.251,
                0.616,
                0.772,
                0.646
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\frac {f (1 - 0) + f (1 + 0)}{2} = \\frac {f (1 - 0) + f (- 1 + 0)}{2} = \\frac {1 + 2}{2} = \\frac {3}{2}.\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.06,
                0.655,
                0.202,
                0.681
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(3)【答案】 \\(\\frac{1}{12}\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.09,
                0.687,
                0.595,
                0.715
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 \\(\\int_0^{x^3 -1}f(t)\\mathrm{d}t = x\\) 两边对 \\(x\\) 求导得 \\(3x^{2}f(x^{3} - 1) = 1\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.091,
                0.725,
                0.294,
                0.751
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "取 \\(x = 2\\) 得 \\(f(7) = \\frac{1}{12}\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.06,
                0.76,
                0.194,
                0.774
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（4）【答案】 40."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.09,
                0.781,
                0.465,
                0.795
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 由 \\(\\mathbf{A} + \\mathbf{B} = (\\pmb {\\alpha} + \\pmb {\\beta},2\\pmb{\\gamma}_2,2\\pmb{\\gamma}_3,2\\pmb{\\gamma}_4)\\) 得"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.098,
                0.803,
                0.699,
                0.838
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\begin{array}{l} \\left| \\boldsymbol {A} + \\boldsymbol {B} \\right| = \\left| \\boldsymbol {\\alpha} + \\boldsymbol {\\beta}, 2 \\gamma_ {2}, 2 \\gamma_ {3}, 2 \\gamma_ {4} \\right| = 8 \\left| \\boldsymbol {\\alpha} + \\boldsymbol {\\beta}, \\gamma_ {2}, \\gamma_ {3}, \\gamma_ {4} \\right| \\\\ = 8 \\left(\\left| \\boldsymbol {\\alpha}, \\boldsymbol {\\gamma} _ {2}, \\boldsymbol {\\gamma} _ {3}, \\boldsymbol {\\gamma} _ {4} \\right| + \\left| \\boldsymbol {\\beta}, \\boldsymbol {\\gamma} _ {2}, \\boldsymbol {\\gamma} _ {3}, \\boldsymbol {\\gamma} _ {4} \\right|\\right) = 8 \\left(\\left| \\boldsymbol {A} \\right| + \\left| \\boldsymbol {B} \\right|\\right) = 4 0. \\\\ \\end{array}\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "bbox": [
                0.06,
                0.844,
                0.148,
                0.859
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "三、选择题"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.06,
                0.865,
                0.205,
                0.879
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(1)【答案】 (B)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.887,
                0.653,
                0.901
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】因为 \\(f(x)\\) 在 \\(x = x_0\\) 处可导，所以 \\(f(x)\\) 在 \\(x = x_0\\) 处可微，"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.09,
                0.91,
                0.931,
                0.935
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "于是 \\(\\mathrm{dy} = f^{\\prime}(x_0)\\Delta x = \\frac{1}{2}\\Delta x\\) ，故函数在 \\(x = x_0\\) 处的微分 \\(\\mathrm{dy}\\) 是与 \\(\\Delta x\\) 同阶而非等价的无穷小，应选(B)."
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.064,
                0.073,
                0.212,
                0.087
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（2）【答案】（A）."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.091,
                0.093,
                0.757,
                0.108
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】将 \\(x = x_0\\) 代入 \\(y'' - 2y' + 4y = 0\\) ，得 \\(f''(x_0) - 2f'(x_0) + 4f(x_0) = 0\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.091,
                0.116,
                0.808,
                0.13
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "从而 \\(f^{\\prime \\prime}(x_0) = -4f(x_0) < 0\\) ，由极值判别法得 \\(x = x_{0}\\) 为 \\(f(x)\\) 的极大值点，应选(A)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.062,
                0.139,
                0.21,
                0.153
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "(3)【答案】 (C)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.092,
                0.161,
                0.254,
                0.175
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 由奇偶性得"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.092,
                0.181,
                0.671,
                0.219
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\(\\iiint_{\\Omega_1}x\\mathrm{d}v = \\iiint_{\\Omega_1}y\\mathrm{d}v = 0,\\quad \\iiint_{\\Omega_1}z\\mathrm{d}v = 4\\iiint_{\\Omega_2}z\\mathrm{d}v,\\quad \\iiint_{\\Omega_1}xyz\\mathrm{d}v = 0\\) 显然选(C)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.064,
                0.224,
                0.21,
                0.238
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（4）【答案】 （B）."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.091,
                0.248,
                0.521,
                0.279
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 因为级数 \\(\\sum_{n = 0}^{\\infty}a_n(x - 1)^n\\) 在 \\(x = -1\\) 处收敛，"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.284,
                0.394,
                0.298
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "所以其收敛半径 \\(R \\geqslant |-1 - 1| = 2\\)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.306,
                0.75,
                0.32
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "当 \\(x = 2\\) 时，因为 \\(|2 - 1| = 1 < R\\) ，所以该级数在 \\(x = 2\\) 处绝对收敛，应选(B)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.064,
                0.328,
                0.21,
                0.342
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "（5）【答案】 (D)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.351,
                0.216,
                0.365
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "【解】 方法一"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.372,
                0.604,
                0.387
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "若 \\(\\alpha_{1},\\alpha_{2},\\dots ,\\alpha_{s}\\) 线性相关，则存在不全为零的数 \\(k_{1},k_{2},\\dots ,k_{s}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.094,
                0.395,
                0.56,
                0.409
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "使得 \\(k_{1}\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1} + k_{2}\\pmb{\\alpha}_{2} + \\dots +k_{s}\\pmb{\\alpha}_{s} = \\mathbf{0},\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.419,
                0.821,
                0.447
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "不妨设 \\(k_{1} \\neq 0\\)，则 \\(\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1} = -\\frac{k_{2}}{k_{1}}\\pmb{\\alpha}_{2} - \\dots - \\frac{k_{s}}{k_{1}}\\pmb{\\alpha}_{s}\\)，即至少有一个向量可由其余向量线性表示，"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.456,
                0.938,
                0.493
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "故 \\(\\alpha_{1},\\alpha_{2},\\dots ,\\alpha_{s}\\) 线性无关的充分必要条件是 \\(\\alpha_{1},\\alpha_{2},\\dots ,\\alpha_{s}\\) 中任意一个向量都不可由其余向量线性表示，应选(D)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.095,
                0.501,
                0.157,
                0.515
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "方法二"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.524,
                0.938,
                0.604
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\(\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1} = \\begin{pmatrix} 1 \\\\ 0 \\\\ 0 \\end{pmatrix}, \\pmb{\\alpha}_{2} = \\begin{pmatrix} 0 \\\\ 1 \\\\ 0 \\end{pmatrix}, \\pmb{\\alpha}_{3} = \\begin{pmatrix} 1 \\\\ 1 \\\\ 0 \\end{pmatrix}\\), 显然 \\(2\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1} + \\pmb{\\alpha}_{2} - \\pmb{\\alpha}_{3} \\neq \\mathbf{0}\\) 且其中任两个向量线性无关, 但向量组 \\(\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1}, \\pmb{\\alpha}_{2}, \\pmb{\\alpha}_{3}\\) 线性相关, 排除(A), (B);"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.093,
                0.613,
                0.938,
                0.692
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\(\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1} = \\begin{pmatrix} 1 \\\\ 0 \\\\ 0 \\end{pmatrix}, \\pmb{\\alpha}_{2} = \\begin{pmatrix} 0 \\\\ 1 \\\\ 0 \\end{pmatrix}, \\pmb{\\alpha}_{3} = \\begin{pmatrix} 0 \\\\ 0 \\\\ 0 \\end{pmatrix}\\), 显然 \\(\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1}\\) 不可由 \\(\\pmb{\\alpha}_{2}, \\pmb{\\alpha}_{3}\\) 线性表示, 但 \\(\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1}, \\pmb{\\alpha}_{2}, \\pmb{\\alpha}_{3}\\) 线性相关, 排除(C), 应选(D)."
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.064,
                0.702,
                0.467,
                0.729
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "四、【解】 \\(\\frac{\\partial u}{\\partial x} = f^{\\prime}\\left(\\frac{x}{y}\\right) + g\\left(\\frac{y}{x}\\right) - \\frac{y}{x} g^{\\prime}\\left(\\frac{y}{x}\\right),\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.09,
                0.737,
                0.79,
                0.767
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\frac {\\partial^ {2} u}{\\partial x ^ {2}} = \\frac {1}{y} f ^ {\\prime \\prime} \\left(\\frac {x}{y}\\right) - \\frac {y}{x ^ {2}} g ^ {\\prime} \\left(\\frac {y}{x}\\right) + \\frac {y}{x ^ {2}} g ^ {\\prime} \\left(\\frac {y}{x}\\right) + \\frac {y ^ {2}}{x ^ {3}} g ^ {\\prime \\prime} \\left(\\frac {y}{x}\\right) = \\frac {1}{y} f ^ {\\prime \\prime} \\left(\\frac {x}{y}\\right) + \\frac {y ^ {2}}{x ^ {3}} g ^ {\\prime \\prime} \\left(\\frac {y}{x}\\right),\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.091,
                0.777,
                0.838,
                0.807
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\frac {\\partial^ {2} u}{\\partial x \\partial y} = - \\frac {x}{y ^ {2}} f ^ {\\prime \\prime} \\left(\\frac {x}{y}\\right) + \\frac {1}{x} g ^ {\\prime} \\left(\\frac {y}{x}\\right) - \\frac {1}{x} g ^ {\\prime} \\left(\\frac {y}{x}\\right) - \\frac {y}{x ^ {2}} g ^ {\\prime \\prime} \\left(\\frac {y}{x}\\right) = - \\frac {x}{y ^ {2}} f ^ {\\prime \\prime} \\left(\\frac {x}{y}\\right) - \\frac {y}{x ^ {2}} g ^ {\\prime \\prime} \\left(\\frac {y}{x}\\right),\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.091,
                0.815,
                0.729,
                0.845
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "则 \\(x\\frac{\\partial^2u}{\\partial x^2} +y\\frac{\\partial^2u}{\\partial x\\partial y} = \\frac{x}{y} f''\\left(\\frac{x}{y}\\right) + \\frac{y^2}{x^2} g''\\left(\\frac{y}{x}\\right) - \\frac{x}{y} f''\\left(\\frac{x}{y}\\right) - \\frac{y^2}{x^2} g''\\left(\\frac{y}{x}\\right) = 0.\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.062,
                0.854,
                0.609,
                0.868
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "五、【解】 特征方程为 \\(\\lambda^2 - 3\\lambda + 2 = 0\\)，特征根为 \\(\\lambda_1 = 1, \\lambda_2 = 2\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.09,
                0.877,
                0.489,
                0.891
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\(y^{\\prime \\prime} - 3y^{\\prime} + 2y = 0\\) 的通解为 \\(y = C_{1}\\mathrm{e}^{x} + C_{2}\\mathrm{e}^{2x}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.091,
                0.9,
                0.518,
                0.914
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "设原方程的特解为 \\( y_0(x) = ax\\mathrm{e}^x \\)，代入得 \\( a = -2 \\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.091,
                0.923,
                0.638,
                0.937
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "故原方程的通解为 \\( y = C_{1} \\mathrm{e}^{x} + C_{2} \\mathrm{e}^{2x} - 2x \\mathrm{e}^{x} \\) (\\( C_{1}, C_{2} \\) 为任意常数)."
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.086,
                0.072,
                0.528,
                0.086
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "因为曲线 \\( y = y(x) \\) 经过点(0,1)，所以 \\( C_1 + C_2 = 1 \\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.095,
                0.613,
                0.108
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\(y = y(x)\\) 在 \\(x = 0\\) 处切线的斜率为 \\(k = (2x - 1)\\mid_{x = 0} = -1\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.086,
                0.117,
                0.763,
                0.13
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "又由 \\( y' = C_1 e^x + 2C_2 e^{2x} - 2(x + 1) e^x \\)，得 \\( C_1 + 2C_2 - 2 = -1 \\)，即 \\( C_1 + 2C_2 = 1 \\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.087,
                0.14,
                0.526,
                0.152
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "从而 \\(C_1 = 1, C_2 = 0\\)，故所求函数为 \\(y = (1 - 2x)\\mathrm{e}^x\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.058,
                0.162,
                0.45,
                0.178
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "六、【解】设 \\(M(x,y)\\) ，则 \\(\\overrightarrow{MA} = \\{-x,1 - y\\}\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "equation",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.187,
                0.46,
                0.219
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\overrightarrow {M A} ^ {0} = \\boldsymbol {F} ^ {0} = \\frac {1}{\\sqrt {x ^ {2} + (1 - y) ^ {2}}} \\{- x, 1 - y \\},\n\\]"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.086,
                0.23,
                0.57,
                0.266
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "则 \\(F(x,y) = |F|\\cdot F^0 = \\frac{k}{[x^2 + (1 - y)^2]^{\\frac{3}{2}}}\\{-x,1 - y\\} ,\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.277,
                0.668,
